name: Meerkat Shares
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
"MSHARE is a part of Mad Meerkat Finance and is a token that helps SVN maintain its peg to MMF. MSHARE holders are rewarded with SVN during periods of network expansion.

See https://mmfinance.gitbook.io/savanna-finance/protocol/tokens"
